      <title>Ocado 股价暴跌 65% 后，长期看涨者放弃投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ocado-s-long-standing-bull-gives-up-after-65-share-price-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位支持 Ocado Group Plc 两年多的分析师改变了对该股的评级，称鉴于项目延迟和流动性挑战，这家在线杂货公司需要“认真考虑其选择”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ocado-s-long-standing-bull-gives-up-after-65-share-price-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:36:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
