      <title>摩根大通启动盈利后首次大型银行债券发售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/jpmorgan-kicks-off-first-of-post-earnings-big-bank-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司在公布第二季度业绩后，成为美国六大银行中第一家进入投资级债券市场的银行，为华尔街预期的大批债券发行打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/jpmorgan-kicks-off-first-of-post-earnings-big-bank-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国即将卸任的政府暂停提高电价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-government-suspends-power-tariff-increase-regulator-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国即将卸任的政府暂停了原定于下个月上调的输配电电价，并敦促能源监管机构确保价格稳定，直到用户能够从近期电力成本的下降中受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-government-suspends-power-tariff-increase-regulator-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普竞选连任推动媒体股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/truth-social-trump-media-shares-soar-after-attack-boosts-reelection-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，前总统唐纳德·特朗普遭到暗杀，但未遂事件为市场上所谓的“特朗普交易”增添了动力，周一早盘，唐纳德·特朗普媒体公司的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/truth-social-trump-media-shares-soar-after-attack-boosts-reelection-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:08:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普攻击油价并关注中国经济数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普遭遇暗杀后，油价震荡上涨或下跌，而中国公布的经济数据更为疲弱，给北京方面带来更大压力，要求其在本周的重要政策会议上增强信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员押注特朗普回归，美国收益率曲线趋陡：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在遭遇暗杀后，投资者加大对唐纳德·特朗普将赢得总统大选的押注，导致美国股指期货上涨，长期债券价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
